    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK888">
<l>aramporuta poṉpōlat tēyu muramporu</l>
<l>tuṭpakai yuṟṟa kuṭi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>A family subject to internal hatred will wear out and lose its strength like iron that has been filed away.</l>
            </lg>
